<plot>Myrto is an eight year old girl, who lives with her young parents in a big city. The pursuit of their career life has made Myrto's parents more distant towards her. Trapped in this situation, in the seemingly real world of adults, Myrto is trying to create a different,an imaginary world, a world inspired by her toys and fairy tales. She dreams, she wakes up and maybe she manages to escape from the adult's «paper world» and succeeds in getting to her own imaginary world, that perhaps is finally more real and tangible...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?018574</url></doc>
